DiagnosisDescription: Rotator cuff syndrome of shoulder and allied disorders
Other and unspecified disc disorder of lumbar region
Routine general medical examination at a health care facility
Tear of medial cartilage or meniscus of knee current
Nonspecific elevation of levels of transaminase or lactic acid dehydrogenase [LDH]
Thoracic or lumbosacral neuritis or radiculitis unspecified
